{
  "stem": "1765.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, social activity sounds like a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] structured [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] concept.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have social activities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to get to school was sometimes very difficult because it was, after all, Siberia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the storms were constant, and we walked in single file with-- with changing the person in the lead every few minutes, so that the wind hit one person for just a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would have like, chains, pick each other up to-- to go to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we were in school, we were cold a lot of the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to sit with our gloves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was not well heated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And just getting through a school day was-- was a major undertaking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't just learning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was learning in an atmosphere that made it very difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No paper, no textbooks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We shared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to share a pencil to do homework, to do-- take notes in school, between lines, around pages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By the time we came home from school, I don't believe was ever before 4:00 or 4:30 in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We came home, not just I, all of the students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had chores to do at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we lived with one of the people, I had to milk the cow for the-- for the people we lived with.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wasn't a very good milkmaid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had to straighten, you know, clean the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't-- you didn't have a vacuum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You had a broom, and you swept, and you straightened up, and you just-- and started the meal and did homework.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So there was very little socializing for people during the week.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
